  06 Sep 2009; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org> libsoundgen-0.6.ebuild:
  Remove redundant IUSE expansion.
  Use eautoreconf to fix makefile problems.
  Remove configure check of unneeded gtk-doc.
  Add RDEPEND on glib instead of libgpewidget.
  Add DEPEND on esound, see #283748 , reported by Ron Widler.
  Add missing docs to GPE_DOCS.

*libsoundgen-0.6 (06 Mar 2009)

  06 Mar 2009; <solar@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml, +libsoundgen-0.6.ebuild:
  - initial commit

